Class MediaInfo.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • tv.matchstick.flint.MediaInfo.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    MediaInfo

    public static class MediaInfo.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    MediaInfo builder, used to set all staffs of MediaInfo. MediaInfo is used by RemoteMediaPlayer to load media on the receiver application.
